clause.text:
identifying the
				specific provision of subsection (d)(2)(B) under which the entity is exempt
				from the requirements under paragraphs (1), (2), and (3);

subparagraph.text:
willfully failing
				to provide complete or updated beneficial ownership information to a State or
				formation agent;

clause.text:
